\ul\b\i\fs24 About\par
\par
\ulnone\b0\i0\fs20 This patch is for the Official BIS Mapper Program which creates maps for the game Fallout 2. It modifies the "mapper2.exe" in memory for the purposes of increasing the visual resolution. It can also be used to create scroll border config files for use with both the Fallout and Fallout2 Hi-Res Patches.\par
\par
It was compiled with "Visual C++ 6.0 -sp6" and should work on most versions of Windows.\par
