\ul\b Original scroll blockers won\rquote t work with the Hi-Res Patch installed.\ulnone\i\par
\b0\i0 The original scroll blockers are disabled in the Hi-res patches. Check the "Map Edges" section of this read-me for details. To setup and test the original scroll blockers, Click the top menu, Click [Settings] then Click [Scroll Blocker Mode]. Click [Yes] to enable the original scroll blockers at 640x480 resolution and reboot. Hi-res mapping can be re-enabled via the same method.\par
